When working in AiNative or repos using this OS:

- Architecture spec: `ENGINEERING-OS.md`
- PR review: follow `docs/1. systems/pr-review-system.md`; prompts in `docs/8. agents/pr-reviewer/` — run Phase 1.5 architecture compliance for feature PRs in existing subsystems
- Task grooming / meetings: `docs/8. agents/task-groomer/`
- Multi-file features: follow PIV — `docs/2. ai-workflows/agentic-coding.md`. Plan + Implementation via `docs/8. agents/specs-planner/` (specs.md); Validation via `docs/8. agents/critic/` and `docs/8. agents/tester/`
- Multi-client releases: `docs/1. systems/client-compatibility-system.md` — pair with release management; run pre-tag check and post-deploy monitor
- Commands and setup: `docs/3. reference/` — navigate by domain, do not guess
- Local shared databases (Docker): `docs/3. reference/setup/local-shared-services.md` — compose at `/Users/emad/docker-infrastructure/docker-compose.yml`
- After hard bugs: append to `docs/4. debugging/<domain>/` using `docs/4. debugging/template.md`
- Significant decisions: new ADR in `docs/6. decisions/` using `docs/6. decisions/template.md`
- Raw capture during work: write to `scratch/` (gitignored); promote on Friday review

Commits: Conventional Commits, short messages (see Commit-style rule).
